{"tid":915813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打記得Big4年代嘅英超頂薪係幾多？","createTime":"2018-11-25T08:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T11:51:30.000Z","uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3daf73191e89023b7e0221c976e8174aa35459","tid":915813,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"而家媒體好關注球員週薪 尤其曼城崛起之後<br />\n耶耶托尼22萬、朗尼26萬、山齊士50萬<br />\n呢啲破紀錄頂薪大家都耳熟能詳<br />\n<br />\n但有冇巴打記得Big4年代 (雲加、費格遜、侯利亞/賓尼迪斯、雲尼亞里/摩連奴) 嗰七八年<br />\n頂薪係幾錢人工 同埋有邊幾個？<br />\n<br />\n記得轉會費紀錄就係李奧keep咗好多年<br />\n3300萬鎊左右去曼聯<br />\n但人工真係冇印象<br />\n應該係華朗李奧呢啲？再後期少少係軍刀波叔？"},{"pid":"90de68be841804f7c6f8a5f2b724aeaa480aca18","tid":915813,"uid":132262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"泰利13萬已經英超最高"},{"pid":"203959ff5ba8bedca96e513e9b7ef8d108fc73d2","tid":915813,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"Fm08定10<br />\n好似法比/朗尼之類都係1xxk周薪<br />\n<br />\n應該20萬封頂啦，big4每隊2-3個1x萬，大部分都係10萬樓下"},{"pid":"0e3afddd690c9fd00e9c005891ba80809e182005","tid":915813,"uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90de68be841804f7c6f8a5f2b724aeaa480aca18","tid":915813,"uid":132262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"泰利13萬已經英超最高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打<br />\n泰利頂薪我都有啲印象<br />\n如果冇記錯應該係後摩連奴時代<br />\n咁你記唔記得大約阿仙奴不敗嗰期係邊個 同埋大約係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22712bffe4f261f4ccd85a0c471a17b02e863181","tid":915813,"uid":206801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"記得費托 謝老4 12-14萬 10年前"},{"pid":"92bbdccefd1acbe4343287f1e3115e5ab9a60cef","tid":915813,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"週薪真高其實係車仔係咩人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebf9ec